<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id0ded9d63-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s4501"><num value="4501">§ 4501.</num><heading> Purpose</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">It is the purpose of this chapter to establish the James Madison Fellowship Program which is designed to encourage graduate study of the American Constitution, its roots, its formation, its principles, and its development.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id0ded9d64-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795">(<ref href="/us/pl/99/500/s101/b/tVIII/s802">Pub. L. 99–500, § 101(b) [title VIII, § 802]</ref>, <date date="1986-10-18">Oct. 18, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/1783-39">100 Stat. 1783–39</ref>, 1783–76, and <ref href="/us/pl/99/591/s101/b/tVIII/s802">Pub. L. 99–591, § 101(b) [title VIII, § 802]</ref>, <date date="1986-10-30">Oct. 30, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/3341-39">100 Stat. 3341–39</ref>, 3341–76.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id0ded9d65-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id0ded9d66-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id0ded9d67-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/99/591">Pub. L. 99–591</ref> is a corrected version of <ref href="/us/pl/99/500">Pub. L. 99–500</ref>.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id0ded9d68-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="shortTitle" id="id0ded9d69-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Short Title</heading><p><ref href="/us/pl/99/500/s101/b/tVIII/s801">Pub. L. 99–500, § 101(b) [title VIII, § 801]</ref>, <date date="1986-10-18">Oct. 18, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/1783-39">100 Stat. 1783–39</ref>, 1783–76, and <ref href="/us/pl/99/591/s101/b/tVIII/s801">Pub. L. 99–591, § 101(b) [title VIII, § 801]</ref>, <date date="1986-10-30">Oct. 30, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/3341-39">100 Stat. 3341–39</ref>, 3341–76, provided that: <quotedContent origin="/us/pl/99/591/s101/b/tVIII/s801">“This title [enacting this chapter] may be cited as the ‘James Madison Memorial Fellowship Act’.”</quotedContent>
</p>
</note>
